content.faq_desc: Everything you need to know about trials, plans, and billing.

faq.q: How does the 30-day free trial work?
faq.a: You get full access to the Basic plan for 30 days. We verify your venue profile, and you won't be charged until the trial ends. You can cancel anytime.

faq.q: What payment methods do you accept?
faq.a: We accept all major credit cards including Visa, Mastercard, and Amex for monthly software subscriptions.

faq.q: Am I locked into a contract?
faq.a: No. Our software plan is month-to-month with no lock-in contracts. You can upgrade your setup or cancel your service at any time.

faq.q: Can I use my own iPad?
faq.a: Yes! Poble runs on any standard iPad (7th Gen or later). If you need hardware, you can purchase our professional hardware bundles.

content.title: Seamless Setup & Ongoing Support.
content.description: Getting started is simple with our guided installation process. And once you're live, our expert team is available 7 days a week.

faq.q: I'm already using a POS. Is switching complicated?
faq.a: We make it seamless. Our support team is here to guide you through the transition and ensure you're ready to trade without stress.
You can use standard iPads you may already own. For reliability, we supply and recommend POSBANK receipt printers, ensuring your hardware works perfectly together from day one.

faq.q: Is it hard to set up my menu?
faq.a: No. We help you with the initial configuration and show you exactly how to manage your items, so you can make updates easily whenever you need to.

faq.q: How long does it take staff to learn the system?
faq.a: We've stripped away the clutter found in older systems. Because it looks and feels like a modern app, staff pick it up intuitively, significantly reducing training time.

faq.q: What happens if my internet disconnects?
faq.a: You can keep taking orders because poble is built to handle local interruptions, allowing you to continue service. Data syncs automatically as soon as you're back online.

faq.q: What kind of support do you provide?
faq.a: Our expert team is based in Australia and available 7 days a week. Whether you need help with a menu update or technical support during a rush, we're here to ensure your venue runs smoothly.
